{"tid":2510362,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"大事件！綠惡魔成為漫威第四階段大反派？！","createTime":"2021-04-30T06:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T07:18:50.000Z","uid":237062,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7685e9a1caac5b0466521e2bfc6078c3b2f7ad24","tid":2510362,"uid":237062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:18:56.000Z","msg":"薩諾斯作為漫威&ldquo;無限之戰&rdquo;階段的最終大反派，給粉絲留下了深刻的印象，如今漫威邁入第四階段，誰又將接替薩諾斯成為新階段的幕後黑手？如今似乎已經有了答案！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmecjBwAztSKFudX5RDWN1nSy7hxJQfJM9t9SwXiUpdieV?filename=9XkjhFD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9XkjhFD.png&h=57fe178a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據That Hashtag Show爆料稱，威廉&middot;達佛飾演的老版&ldquo;綠惡魔&rdquo;諾曼&middot;奧斯朋會成為MCU第四階段的主要反派，而他也會在《蜘蛛人3：無家日》中率先登場，並且不會是那種一次性反派，而更偏向薩諾斯那種貫穿整個系列的階段性反派。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPEmmriYM7oQvsk7suhdZHJMpjz8fe9Udv7dZ6eEzfoyE?filename=gk9Dyed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgk9Dyed.png&h=8f115ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n並且報導提到，作為主要反派的諾曼&middot;奧斯朋來自其他平行宇宙，而因為多元宇宙的開啟，導致他干擾到了MCU彼得&middot;帕克的生活，致使小蜘蛛不得不開始調查自己宇宙的諾曼&middot;奧斯朋，由此引出MCU的奧斯朋。<br />\n<br />\n而MCU版諾曼&middot;奧斯朋看起來並不是一個惡棍，他有政治抱負，做慈善，甚至還支持復仇者聯盟，成為其背後最大的金主。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmciVNdz8dqjZyU8X5MWXcfmmWzE1NJY5mnnAKagamHGNB?filename=DZ48a1o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZ48a1o.png&h=c8c13b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據報導，漫威影業的想法是，在不同的宇宙裡英雄和反派不能保證會走上完全相同的道路，漫威打算深度探索諾曼&middot;奧斯朋這個角色，在他還沒有黑化成綠惡魔的情況下，他會給MCU帶來怎樣的故事，當然不保證未來他不會黑化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZJDXkvxKWH35fGLx9UZC5e3WqK8UJ3GPYj9neBdiCqw8?filename=peNQ8Oj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpeNQ8Oj.png&h=8ad6b2ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，之前也說過，《獵鷹冬兵》的結尾原打算讓奧斯朋提前登場，但由於當時的版權和時長問題放棄了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc3me5oxqx8xrfxhbKraTZ1ZkcV1ap99S3TRFHQ4g1t55?filename=fAnJKmV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfAnJKmV.png&h=919caeef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但隨著上周迪士尼和SONY簽署了大範圍合作協議，使得SONY的影視庫可以登錄迪士尼旗下串流媒體平台，兩家的關係得以提升，也使得威廉&middot;達佛版綠惡魔可以加入MCU。<br />\n<br />\n並且此前也有消息爆出，威廉&middot;達佛已經加入了荷蘭弟的《蜘蛛人3》，預計會在片中以彩蛋的形式客串登場，以及未來也有可能在多部其他電影和Disney+劇集裡出場<br />\n<br />\n《蜘蛛人3：無家日》計劃於12月17日在北美公映。"},{"pid":"8b823c36bcff8e9c0f4647a425967dac67ad84e1","tid":2510362,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:20:04.000Z","msg":"JOHN WICK宇宙?"},{"pid":"091444ca135115fb92e8e9db7a181938662f926e","tid":2510362,"uid":139791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"咁佢DC個角色點算"},{"pid":"ba561074deeda782cabf24c9a939a15f682d2c6f","tid":2510362,"uid":198688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"091444ca135115fb92e8e9db7a181938662f926e","tid":2510362,"uid":139791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"咁佢DC個角色點算"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:47:14.000Z","msg":"不如叫Amber Heard辭演仲實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae7a87400733bbbb7b7463eb7e12b0e13bab416","tid":2510362,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba561074deeda782cabf24c9a939a15f682d2c6f","tid":2510362,"uid":198688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"091444ca135115fb92e8e9db7a181938662f926e","tid":2510362,"uid":139791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"咁佢DC個角色點算"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:47:14.000Z","msg":"不如叫Amber Heard辭演仲實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T06:49:05.000Z","msg":"Fantastic Bitch點會辭演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c41cf4f9ae00e35f45bb5b38e9ce3750e5fad83","tid":2510